66 Rundle Street was completed in 2009 and was built to the highest standards. For the first time since its completion, the opportunity exists to lease two tenancies, one featuring fully fitted space whilst the other provides a refurbished open plan area.

The owner has recently completed a full refurbishment of the main entry into the building which has provided a greater first impression to the entrance into this high quality asset.

Arguably the most prominent building in all of Kent Town, located on the Corner of Rundle Street and The Parade West, close to the CBD and offering all the amenity including shops and cafe's that the traditional fringe locations lack.

There are good numbers of onsite parking available and there is ample, timed street parking for visitors and staff overflow alike.

Lease Term: Negotiable 
Options: Negotiable
Rent Reviews: Negotiable
Available: Immediately 

*approximately

Located within a short walking distance to Adelaide CBD, 29 Dequetteville Terrace Kent Town oozes charm.

Offered with Parkland views and Boulevard exposure to Dequetteville Terrace, it is perfectly located for ease into the CBD and also into the eastern suburbs. 

With up to 390m² available, it is a combination of both open plan and well appointed offices/meeting rooms. 

The tenancy also offers up to 15 secure, on-site carparks and the ability to enjoy a beautiful garden setting. 

Areas-  390m² available.

A hidden gem, 1-5 Wakefield Street Kent Town is a high quality, modern office building featuring full height windows around the perimeter of the building that allow for maximum natural light penetration.

Two tenancies are now available - Ground floor of 303 sqm and first floor of 403 sqm. The ground floor tenancy provides an existing fitout comprising a reception area, boardroom, meeting room, three (3) offices and large open plan area suitable for workstations. The first floor tenancy is completely open plan allowing fitout flexibility. The owner is willing to modify to suit.

Located in the leafy inner eastern fringe and offering easy access to the CBD and surrounding suburbs, 1-5 Wakefield Street, Kent Town is unlike other main stream fringe locations – in addition to the designated basement parking for staff, the building enjoys excellent street parking that, while restricted in the main to a 2 hr time limit, offers that valuable additional parking for staff and easy access for clients visiting. 

The building has a unique, architectural design that will offer the ascending tenant the opportunity to locate their business in one of the best properties the fringe market has to offer.

Lease Term: Negotiable
Options: Negotiable 
Rent Reviews: Negotiable 
Available: Immediately

*Approximately

97 King William Street Kent Town is without a doubt the best office building in Kent Town. Completed in 2020, the devlopment over 4 levels is a terrific example of contemporary, on-trend office accommodation. Designed with balconies on the Northern and Southern faces, featuring glass sliding doors balconies to create indoor outdoor flow and ventilation, the space is perfect for the modern office tenant seeking a light and bright work environment. 

Whole floor of 330 square metres is available with smaller tenancies from 145sqm and 220sqm also on offer for tenants. All open plan, the building has been designed to maximise flexibility and efficiency with a tenant’s fitout.

All floors are accessible by lift and are provided with an open-plan kitchen, stylish bathrooms and shower. Onsite secure basement car parking and bike parking are available for the occupiers.
